<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_519_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> VVılhelm . Vns hat <expan>furg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> pruder <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_519_r1l4">Grünſfelt parfuſſen oꝛdens hie beẏ vns . vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_519_r1l5">Jr Jm droet . Alſo . daʒ er vor euch vnſicher ſeẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_519_r1l6">darümb daʒ Er einem ewrem hinterſeſſen hie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_519_r1l7">mit dem rehten <expan>cʒugeſproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab . das vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_519_r1l8">etvvaʒ von euch vnglımpflich dunkt <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_519_r1l9">den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> pruder <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan> v̈mb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıchern </ab>
